Useful snippets

(env)$ python manage.py makemigrations --dry-run --verbosity 3
to dryrun model changes(migrations)

(env)$ python manage.py test
to run test


get_user_model() when you need to import the User model to query it. E.g.
User = get_user_model()
User.objects.filter(...)
settings.AUTH_USER_MODEL when you need to referencing User model in ForeignKey, ManyToManyField or OneToOneField. E.g.
class MyModel(models.Model):
    user = models.ForeignKey(settings.AUTH_USER_MODEL)get_user_model() when you need to import the User model to query it. E.g.
    User = get_user_model()
    User.objects.filter(...)
settings.AUTH_USER_MODEL when you need to referencing User model in ForeignKey, ManyToManyField or OneToOneField. E.g.
class MyModel(models.Model):
    user = models.ForeignKey(settings.AUTH_USER_MODEL)